measurements.description: Thirteen slightly cupped flowers on one 68-cm arching inflorescence; sepals obovate, yellow speckled burgundy; petals eliptical, yellow, speckled burgundy, burgundy midrib; lip white overlaid burgundy reverse, marked burgundy heavily apical third, center burgundy stripe, sparsely spotted burgundy proximal two-thirds, densely speckled burgundy mid-lobe edges, keels yellow spotted burgundy; column yellow, overlaid burgundy, spotted burgundy ventral surface, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
